\[
\left[\left(\Conj{u}v'-\Conj{u}'v\right)p_{0}\right]_{a}^{b}=0\qquad\forall u,v
\]

\end_inset

则算符 
\begin_inset Formula $\Operator{L}$
\end_inset

 关于内积
